flowMgrExtMib.description: This MIB module describes the ArrowPoint Communications enterprise MIB for the flow manager module.

apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceOptions.name: apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceOptions
apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceOptions.description: This object specifies a bitmask of the current flow trace settings.

apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceState.name: apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceState
apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceState.description: This object specifies the current state of flow tracing.

apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceFilename.name: apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceFilename
apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceFilename.description: This object specifies the file name of the log file on disk.

apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceMaxFileSize.name: apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceMaxFileSize
apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceMaxFileSize.description: This object specifies the maximum file length allowed to be saved to the disk.

apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceDuration.name: apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceDuration
apFlowMgrExtFlowTraceDuration.description: This object specifies the duration of the Flow Tracing logging session in seconds.

apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort1.name: apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort1
apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort1.description: This object specifies the first destination tcp port number for flows that the flow manager will not reclaim.

apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort2.description: This object specifies the second destination tcp port number for flows that the flow manager will not reclaim.

apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort3.name: apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort3
apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort3.description: This object specifies the third destination tcp port number for flows that the flow manager will not reclaim.

apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort4.name: apFlowMgrExtPermanentPort4

apFlowMgrExtReserveCleanTimer.name: apFlowMgrExtReserveCleanTimer
apFlowMgrExtReserveCleanTimer.description: This object specifies the time (in seconds) at which the flow manager scans flows with a source or destination port of less than 25 and may attempt to clean up that flow.

apFlowMgrExtPortIdleTable.name: apFlowMgrExtPortIdleTable
apFlowMgrExtPortIdleTable.description: This is the table of port idle timer values.

apFlowMgrExtPortIdleEntry.name: apFlowMgrExtPortIdleEntry
apFlowMgrExtPortIdleEntry.description: A table containing the port number and associated idle timer.

apFlowMgrExtPortIdle.name: apFlowMgrExtPortIdle
apFlowMgrExtPortIdle.description: This is the port number of the port for which this entry contains the flow manager port configuration.

apFlowMgrExtPortIdleValue.name: apFlowMgrExtPortIdleValue
apFlowMgrExtPortIdleValue.description: This is the flow manager reset idle value for this port.

apFlowMgrExtPortLowWaterFCB.name: apFlowMgrExtPortLowWaterFCB
apFlowMgrExtPortLowWaterFCB.description: This is the configured flow manager FCB low water mark for this port. When free FCBs constitute this percentage of total FCBs, expedited flow recovery procedures are invoked.

apFlowMgrExtIdleTimer.description: This object specifies the time (in seconds) which the flow manager will use to time out flows. A value of 0 indicates that internal values will be used.
